The categories of Race and Hispanic or Latino origin (ethnicity) are very broad and more specific or granular categories are grouped within them.

 

Click the “Specific or Granular Categories” job aid, and you will see how more specific or granular categories are grouped and which category to select in your system when a patient gives you a more specific response.
